{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Disfigure is entirely free to play for the time being, so please consider supporting us through the donation DLC!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In an arena shrouded by darkness, pay keen attention to your surroundings where monsters could be lurking. Choose between circle and cone vision: one allows you to see all around but not far, while the latter allows you to see far in one direction. Survive for as long as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083160/extras/combat.gif?t=1731374847\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Variety of Builds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from over 150 upgrades and weapon perks to create a unique build for each run. Become a pyromaniac, shoot lightning, fire a storm of bullets, or even harness light to destroy your enemies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083160/extras/lightning.gif?t=1731374847\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Variety of Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new weapons with currency earned from runs! Each weapon behaves differently and has its own unique perks allowing for a multitude of different builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083160/extras/weaponselect.gif?t=1731374847\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 maps with 19 unique enemies and 6 bosses in total</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 150 unique upgrades to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15+ weapons each with unique perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Quick restarts with 20 minute runs that can also be played endlessly</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 difficulty modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Online leaderboards<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083160/extras/boss.gif?t=1731374847\" />Please note that NightCafe AI Art Generator was used to create some of the upgrade icons in the game. NightCafe allows people to use it for commercial purposes and does its best to ensure that non-copyrighted images are used for generating art. We're only using it as placeholders right now and working on replacing it!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"SHOTGUN UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"SNIPER UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"KNIFE UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"TWIN KATANAS UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"GREATSWORD UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"SCYTHE UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"LEVER-ACTION RIFLE UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"BURST RIFLE UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"},{"name":"MINIGUN UNLOCKED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2083160/8090cedd8027ff00a8aad1166b150f9ca611defa.jpg"}